{"title":"The Litespeed Pinhoti III Has Longer Travel, Bigger Tires, and More Clearance","link":"https://theradavist.com/2021/04/the-litespeed-pinhoti-iii-has-longer-travel-bigger-tires-and-more-clearance/?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=the-litespeed-pinhoti-iii-has-longer-travel-bigger-tires-and-more-clearance","date":1617634647000,"content":"<p><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1333\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2021/04/pinhotiIII-frame-two-tone_20d8551f-5561-48b0-8e7d-da6385d434d5_2000x.png?fit=1024,9999&amp;quality=75\" alt=\"\" class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-208176\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2021/04/pinhotiIII-frame-two-tone_20d8551f-5561-48b0-8e7d-da6385d434d5_2000x.png?w=2000&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2021/04/pinhotiIII-frame-two-tone_20d8551f-5561-48b0-8e7d-da6385d434d5_2000x.png?resize=1024,682&amp;quality=75 1024w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2021/04/pinhotiIII-frame-two-tone_20d8551f-5561-48b0-8e7d-da6385d434d5_2000x.png?resize=768,512&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2021/04/pinhotiIII-frame-two-tone_20d8551f-5561-48b0-8e7d-da6385d434d5_2000x.png?resize=1800,1200&amp;quality=75 1800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2021/04/pinhotiIII-frame-two-tone_20d8551f-5561-48b0-8e7d-da6385d434d5_2000x.png?resize=1335,890&amp;quality=75 1335w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2021/04/pinhotiIII-frame-two-tone_20d8551f-5561-48b0-8e7d-da6385d434d5_2000x.png?resize=700,467&amp;quality=75 700w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2021/04/pinhotiIII-frame-two-tone_20d8551f-5561-48b0-8e7d-da6385d434d5_2000x.png?resize=1536,1024&amp;quality=75 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px\" /></p>\n<p>Named after the Pinhoti Trail, which extends between Snake Creek Gap and Dug Gap within the Chattahoochee Forest into north Georgia, Litspeed&#8217;s newest iteration of their hardtail, the Pinhoti III, received some modern updates. Now optimized for a 130mm suspension fork, the Pinhoti III also fits a 29&#215;2.6&#8243; or a 27.5&#215;3&#8243; tire, thanks to an asymmetric dropped chainstay and a new CNC-machined titanium chainstay yoke. </p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2394\" height=\"1310\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2021/04/Screen-Shot-2021-04-05-at-8.48.36-AM.png?fit=1024,9999&amp;quality=75\" alt=\"\" class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-208177\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2021/04/Screen-Shot-2021-04-05-at-8.48.36-AM.png?w=2394&amp;quality=75 2394w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2021/04/Screen-Shot-2021-04-05-at-8.48.36-AM.png?resize=1024,560&amp;quality=75 1024w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2021/04/Screen-Shot-2021-04-05-at-8.48.36-AM.png?resize=2000,1094&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2021/04/Screen-Shot-2021-04-05-at-8.48.36-AM.png?resize=768,420&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2021/04/Screen-Shot-2021-04-05-at-8.48.36-AM.png?resize=1800,985&amp;quality=75 1800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2021/04/Screen-Shot-2021-04-05-at-8.48.36-AM.png?resize=1335,731&amp;quality=75 1335w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2021/04/Screen-Shot-2021-04-05-at-8.48.36-AM.png?resize=700,383&amp;quality=75 700w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2021/04/Screen-Shot-2021-04-05-at-8.48.36-AM.png?resize=1536,841&amp;quality=75 1536w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2021/04/Screen-Shot-2021-04-05-at-8.48.36-AM.png?resize=2048,1121&amp;quality=75 2048w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2394px) 100vw, 2394px\" /></p>\n<p>The Geometry has been tweaked as well, with a slacker head angle, longer reach, and a few other tweaks. Litespeed offers various builds (SLX shown here at a retail of $4,270) and finishing kits, and with all these new updates, the size medium frame comes in at just 1,649 grams (size medium)â€”a savings of 95 grams over our previous version of the Pinhoti. As with all Litespeed bikes, these are made in Chattanooga, Tennesee. </p>\n<p>See more at <a href=\"https://litespeed.com/products/pinhoti-iii\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Litespeed</a>.</p>","author":"prolly","siteTitle":"The Radavist","siteHash":"96eb481d8084f04a4602bac57874ba717baf56b758f45547b5caf2312da766ef","entryHash":"1181b2560d53ed0cdf22526fb63ee638195136d65b4cf94f9ceb139508f6a7bc","category":"Cycling"}